## Verification Plan

### Build Check
```bash
wsl -d Ubuntu bash -c "cd /home/amit25/clarivex-solution && npx next build 2>&1"
```
Build must pass with 0 errors.

### Browser Testing (Automated via browser tool)
1. Open `http://localhost:3000` â†’ verify General content shows (no country cookie)
2. Select "US" from navbar â†’ verify ALL sections update to US content (hero, stats, tools, compliance, CTAs)
3. Navigate to `/blog` â†’ verify US blog posts are shown by default, country badge visible
4. Navigate to `/news` â†’ verify only US news shown (no country filter tabs)
5. Select "UK" â†’ verify content changes globally
6. Reload page â†’ verify UK persists (cookie)
7. Check mobile (375px) â†’ verify flags render as images, selector works

### Manual Verification (User)
- Visually confirm content quality for each country version
- Verify flag images display correctly on your Windows machine
